  <div> <span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;">Hi {{{Recipient.FirstName}}},</span></span> 
   <br /> 
   <br /> <span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;">During these trying times, I wanted to make sure that you were doing ok. In general, managing a business is a considerably large task. Coupled with a spread of an outbreak, managing daily operations becomes even more challenging. Business owners and managers now must focus on running their business while ensuring their patrons and employees are kept safe.</span> 
   <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;">Recently, a business’s efforts to reduce health risks in the workplace have been under careful examination from individuals and media outlets. Failing to provide increased hygiene measures can be detrimental to a business. Employees begin to believe their well-being is not a priority and customers form preconceived opinions based on the lack of cleanliness in the facility. Ultimately, poor hygiene measures will decrease revenue and increase absenteeism for a business.</span></span><br /> <br /> <span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;">It is important that businesses now start to think of what they will do to maintain the health of their employees and patrons. <b>Throughout COVID-19 basic preventative hygiene measures prevailed as the best defense against the virus, and businesses must adapt to a preventative outlook to avoid future outbreaks.&nbsp;</b> As we prepare for a life post-pandemic, <i>I want to make sure your business has the proper hygiene resources implemented in your facility.</i></span></span><br /> <br /> <span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;">For over <i>40 </i>years, </span></span><a href="https://www.citronhygiene.com/"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;">Citron Hygiene</span></span></a> <span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;"> has helped businesses combat health risks through preventative hygiene measures. Our services are well thought out to ensure regardless of where a patron is in your facility, their health is maintained. Each part of your facility is unique, and the risks users face while in the washroom are not the same risks they would face at their desks. Citron Hygiene’s services address the risks associated with each area of your facility, reducing the risks of cross-contamination. <b>Our services focus on reducing surface-to-person contact while increasing sanitation and disinfection.</b></span></span><br /> <br /> <span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;">I would like to help your business implement a hygiene plan to keep your workers safe. I am available to set up a Skype meeting at your earliest convenience. Please do not hesitate to reach out if you have any questions.</span></span><br /> <br /> <span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-serif;
